{
  "id": "5-1",
  "title": "Act 1: Survive",
  "startNode": "main",
  "nodes": {
    "main": {
      "events": [
        {
          "type": "marker",
          "id": "ch5_act1_start"
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "blackout",
          "args": {
            "enabled": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "titleCard",
          "args": {
            "text": "Chapter 5: Radiation and Rust"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 2500
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeIn",
          "ms": 1200
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The wasteland's first night was silent.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 16
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 700
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Not quiet—something else. A heavier silence filled with indistinct sounds.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Something was moving in the distance, footsteps unlike any creature they knew. Wind through ruined structures wailed from all directions.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "No Ark ceiling overhead, no pipes, no lights. Only a deep, endless darkness and sparse, radiation-tinted starlight.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1000
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "They found their first shelter in an abandoned building's basement.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Old world architecture—the materials completely different from the Ark, thicker, older. Much had collapsed, but the basement structure remained intact. Could block wind, could shield from the wasteland creatures' visual sensing.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Barely adequate.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 16
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.alea.name}}'s first task was injury assessment.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.elias.name}} had a considerable bruise on his back from the supply station impact—short-term inability to withstand equivalent shock. {{characters.soren.name}} had a shallow cut on his arm, infection risk high in wasteland conditions. {{characters.lyra.name}}'s neural connection overload recovery was slowest; she sat in the corner, hands shaking slightly on her knees.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.alea.name}} opened the medical pack, treated each injury methodically, with minimal conversation.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.soren.name}}",
          "text": "You've done this before.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.alea.name}}",
          "text": "Lower decks. No medicine for injuries, learned to treat myself.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "She secured {{characters.elias.name}}'s back with fixed bandages, pushed anti-inflammatory pills in front of him.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.alea.name}}",
          "text": "Take them.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.elias.name}}",
          "text": "I don't like swallowing pills.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 24
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 300
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.alea.name}}",
          "text": "I know. Take them.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "He did.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 900
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Over the next two days, they systematically searched the surrounding area centered on the ruin.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.soren.name}} mapped terrain, marked resource points and danger zones. {{characters.elias.name}} continuously scanned electronic frequencies, searching for active artificial installations. {{characters.alea.name}} and {{characters.lyra.name}} handled actual searching and supply inventory.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 700
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "On the third day, they found one of the abandoned forward bases—a large cargo hold half-buried in dunes, exterior lock long since rusted away.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 400
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Inside, several crates of expired but still consumable compressed rations, and two sets of backup neural stabilizers, seals intact.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 22
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 700
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.lyra.name}} held those two stabilizer sets to her chest like they were something precious.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 20
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "{{characters.lyra.name}}",
          "text": "Found them.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Her tone was light, but everyone present knew what it meant.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 18
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1800
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeOut",
          "ms": 1200,
          "args": {
            "stay": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "end"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "onComplete": [
    "complete"
  ]
}
